verses.text:
before Ephraim, Benjamin and Manasseh.
Awaken your might;
    come and save us.

Restore us, O God;
    make your face shine on us,
    that we may be saved.

Restore us, God Almighty;
    make your face shine on us,
    that we may be saved.

Restore us, Lord God Almighty;
    make your face shine on us,
    that we may be saved.
